    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_ca4a1107 (line 83428)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_ca4a1107:
    # "Frequently taken by the goblin, and frequently offering herself to him, it was only a matter of time."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_e48fbf69 (line 83435)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_e48fbf69:
    # "The coupling of goblin and human was said to only rarely produce offspring."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_3f3c1329 (line 83436)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_3f3c1329:
    # "But such low chances had been offset by the frequent nature of their mating."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_65f7ff0d (line 83437)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_65f7ff0d:
    # "Her belly began to swell, with passing weaks, more and more."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_0e0142a0 (line 83438)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_0e0142a0:
    # "Her belly expanded, her ankles swole up, and she suffered the morning sickness."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_b16f99e9 (line 83439)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_b16f99e9:
    # "Still, the cage remained her home, though the sweet taste of the drink made it impossible to worry of such things."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_77634fa1 (line 83440)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_77634fa1:
    # "Instead, Sarah laid blissfully on the floor of the cage, lost to blind happiness as she felt her child inside of her."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_6794674b (line 83441)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_6794674b:
    # "The goblin, father to her brood, did not abade in his desire."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_08b9272a (line 83442)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_08b9272a:
    # "And as Sarah grew larger and fatter, rapidly, she became ever more immobile."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_0ff92e54 (line 83443)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_0ff92e54:
    # "She laid, staring up at the night sky, as all the world spun about her, pulsing and dancing to the drink's influence."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_c0239921 (line 83444)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_c0239921:
    # "Soon, she would bear him children."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_ed065895 (line 83445)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_ed065895:
    # "And, she hoped, Gods willing she would give him so many more."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_b554d785 (line 83446)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_b554d785:
    # "So ends the story of Sarah Rose."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_bb55a9fb (line 83447)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_bb55a9fb:
    # "Princess to mage. Traitor to her teacher. Goblin wife."
    ""

# MageInTheRuinsOrc3_99ebcef6 (line 83448)
translate ru MageInTheRuinsOrc3_99ebcef6:
    # "The End."
    ""

